{"tid":1341510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵不顧乘客安全 明天起不應再接載任何乘客","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:42:03.000Z","uid":121139,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dca8193d3372498384b64fe0b17beb98e933f2c5","tid":1341510,"uid":121139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:45:54.000Z","msg":"乘客被襲擊，港鐵完全不負責任<br />\n更於車箱廣播列車暫停服務，任由白衫衝入車箱打人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日起唔可以再比港鐵接載任何乘客，因為你比人打，佢地會自己走晒，理得你地比人打死。<br />\n<br />\n聽日仲諗住搭港鐵番工？<br />\n有良心嘅你。請不要讓市民進入港鐵危險範圍，搭上會受傷害同恐嚇嘅列車"},{"pid":"be51219d20f9b4608e0e9e344a170a6f08d4c1cd","tid":1341510,"uid":232766,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:46:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六大訴求：</span></strong><br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 釋放被捕人士、撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會、並追究警隊濫權<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>追究元朗暴徒行兇、警察失蹤</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e2c50a9eee6c12c69a4f32388628e79f4d202340","tid":1341510,"uid":197640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"LAWSUIT佢啦，腸下股票會唔見幾多"},{"pid":"513bdfbccb0706dc8d52b31352717fb1237b0955","tid":1341510,"uid":121139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:47:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1d653526caa14774df1a4f2a0a6db1b8ac54a40","tid":1341510,"uid":121139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:49:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7298b9aa2830d998911b7701641ee10edcd9db13"